                {
                    "name": "Xilvereks on the Material Plane",
                    "type": "sidebar",
                    "text": "Despite their origins within Gluttondark, xilvireks have been encountered with increasing frequency in the deepest depths of the Darklands, perhaps as a result of botched summonings by xulgath clerics of Zevgavizeb. Whether by chance or through the intent of their creator, xilvireks have begun to stretch their reach beyond the evolutionary nightmare of the Abyss.",
