            "name": "Xilvirek",
            "type": "section",
            "text": "Xilvireks are the result of the strange evolution that takes place in <a aonid=\"82\" game-obj=\"Deities\">Zevgavizeb\u2019s</a> Abyssal realm. These fiends resemble their dread demon lord and claim to be living embodiments of the Lord of Reptiles\u2019s snapping jaws.<br/><br/><b><u><a aonid=\"5\" game-obj=\"Skills\" general=\"true\">Recall Knowledge - Fiend</a></u> (<u><a aonid=\"13\" game-obj=\"Skills\">Religion</a></u>)</b>: DC 32",
